CREATE TABLE [umbracoKeyValue] ([key] NVARCHAR(256) NOT NULL,
[value] NVARCHAR(255) NULL,
[updated] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoKeyValue_updated] DEFAULT (GETDATE()))
ALTER TABLE [umbracoKeyValue] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoKeyValue] PRIMARY KEY ([key])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoUserLogin] ([sessionId] UniqueIdentifier NOT NULL,
[userId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[loggedInUtc] DATETIME NOT NULL,
[lastValidatedUtc] DATETIME NOT NULL,
[loggedOutUtc] DATETIME NULL,
[ipAddress] NVARCHAR(255) NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoUserLogin] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoUserLogin] PRIMARY KEY ([sessionId])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoUserLogin_lastValidatedUtc] ON [umbracoUserLogin] ([lastValidatedUtc])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoUserLogin] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoUserLogin_umbracoUser_id] FOREIGN KEY ([userId]) REFERENCES [umbracoUser] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoConsent] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[current] BIT NOT NULL,
[source] NVARCHAR(512) NOT NULL,
[context] NVARCHAR(128) NOT NULL,
[action] NVARCHAR(512) NOT NULL,
[createDate] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoConsent_createDate] DEFAULT (GETDATE()),
[state] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[comment] NVARCHAR(255) NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoConsent] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoConsent] PRIMARY KEY ([id])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoAudit] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[performingUserId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[performingDetails] NVARCHAR(1024) NULL,
[performingIp] NVARCHAR(64) NULL,
[eventDateUtc] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoAudit_eventDateUtc] DEFAULT (GETDATE()),
[affectedUserId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[affectedDetails] NVARCHAR(1024) NULL,
[eventType] NVARCHAR(256) NOT NULL,
[eventDetails] NVARCHAR(1024) NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoAudit] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoAudit] PRIMARY KEY ([id])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[versionId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[languageId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[name] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
[date] DATETIME NOT NULL,
[availableUserId] INTEGER NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation_VersionId] ON [umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation] ([versionId],[languageId])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation_LanguageId] ON [umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation] ([languageId])

ALTER TABLE [umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation_umbracoContentVersion_id] FOREIGN KEY ([versionId]) REFERENCES [umbracoContentVersion] ([id])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation_umbracoLanguage_id] FOREIGN KEY ([languageId]) REFERENCES [umbracoLanguage] ([id])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoContentVersionCultureVariation_umbracoUser_id] FOREIGN KEY ([availableUserId]) REFERENCES [umbracoUser] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoDocumentCultureVariation] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[nodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[languageId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[edited] BIT NOT NULL,
[available] BIT NOT NULL,
[published] BIT NOT NULL,
[name] NVARCHAR(255) NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoDocumentCultureVariation] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoDocumentCultureVariation] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoDocumentCultureVariation_NodeId] ON [umbracoDocumentCultureVariation] ([nodeId],[languageId])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoContentSchedule] ([id] UniqueIdentifier NOT NULL,
[nodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[languageId] INTEGER NULL,
[date] DATETIME NOT NULL,
